more space exploration?

00:10:19.110 --> 00:10:21.090 align:middle line:84%
>>ZUBRIN: At this point,
there's no action.

00:10:21.090 --> 00:10:24.430 align:middle line:90%
I mean, NASA's on autopilot.

00:10:24.430 --> 00:10:27.540 align:middle line:84%
So, the parts of NASA that
were being competently run,

00:10:27.540 --> 00:10:29.370 align:middle line:84%
which I mentioned
the space astronomy

00:10:29.370 --> 00:10:32.347 align:middle line:84%
program and the robotic
exploration programs,

00:10:32.347 --> 00:10:33.930 align:middle line:84%
they're just kind
of going along doing

00:10:33.930 --> 00:10:35.560 align:middle line:90%
