So, that's OK.

00:10:37.220 --> 00:10:39.420 align:middle line:84%
The problem is, is that
the human spaceflight

00:10:39.420 --> 00:10:41.430 align:middle line:90%
program is aimless.

00:10:41.430 --> 00:10:44.887 align:middle line:84%
So, we're spending,
you know, whatever,

00:10:44.887 --> 00:10:47.220 align:middle line:84%
