00:10:51.990 --> 00:10:52.920 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:10:52.920 --> 00:10:54.419 align:middle line:84%
If you want to
accomplish something,

00:10:54.419 --> 00:10:56.490 align:middle line:90%
