00:11:11.700 --> 00:11:12.110 align:middle line:90%
base program.

00:11:12.110 --> 00:11:12.630 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: There's no plan.

00:11:12.630 --> 00:11:13.713 align:middle line:90%
>>ZUBRIN: There's no plan.

00:11:13.713 --> 00:11:15.660 align:middle line:90%
There's no program.

00:11:15.660 --> 00:11:19.200 align:middle line:84%
And so, you know,
if this goes on

00:11:19.200 --> 00:11:26.900 align:middle line:84%
