aboard the International Space

00:16:26.620 --> 00:16:27.420 align:middle line:10%
Station.

00:16:27.420 --> 00:16:29.430 align:middle line:10%
On board the
orbiting laboratory,

00:16:29.430 --> 00:16:32.820 align:middle line:10%
