every day here on the Station

00:17:04.410 --> 00:17:06.390 align:middle line:10%
as we use this
orbiting laboratory

00:17:06.390 --> 00:17:09.450 align:middle line:10%
as a stepping stone for
future deep space exploration.

00:17:09.450 --> 00:17:12.270 align:middle line:10%
>>NARRATOR: In tandem with
Space Station research,

00:17:12.270 --> 00:17:15.960 align:middle line:10%
NASA will send a robotic
mission to capture and redirect

00:17:15.960 --> 00:17:19.170 align:middle line:10%
