up with such an idea.

00:19:12.450 --> 00:19:12.720 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Why?

00:19:12.720 --> 00:19:15.261 align:middle line:84%
>>ZUBRIN: It was an idea that
they came up with for something

00:19:15.261 --> 00:19:16.110 align:middle line:90%
to do.

00:19:16.110 --> 00:19:17.910 align:middle line:84%
And then they
attempted to justify it

00:19:17.910 --> 00:19:21.170 align:middle line:84%
by saying it's part of the
human Mars mission program.

00:19:21.170 --> 00:19:25.920 align:middle line:84%
