00:19:42.680 --> 00:19:45.710 align:middle line:84%
being supported by
different constituencies out

00:19:45.710 --> 00:19:46.870 align:middle line:90%
of their self-interest.

00:19:46.870 --> 00:19:49.670 align:middle line:84%
And then they justify
them by saying oh, this

