They are doing things
in order to spend money.

00:20:04.607 --> 00:20:05.690 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: That's not smart.

00:20:05.690 --> 00:20:07.760 align:middle line:84%
>>ZUBRIN: No, it's like
running your business

00:20:07.760 --> 00:20:09.920 align:middle line:90%
