00:20:09.920 --> 00:20:13.410 align:middle line:84%
And you know, if you're
running a business,

00:20:13.410 --> 00:20:15.200 align:middle line:90%
you do buy things from vendors.

00:20:15.200 --> 00:20:18.390 align:middle line:84%
But you do that
for your purposes.

00:20:18.390 --> 00:20:20.810 align:middle line:84%
You don't do things
in order to say

00:20:20.810 --> 00:20:22.960 align:middle line:90%
hi vendors, Merry Christmas.

00:20:22.960 --> 00:20:26.570 align:middle line:84%
We've decided to do
something to make you happy.

00:20:26.570 --> 00:20:31.700 align:middle line:84%
So, what's needed is for NASA
to say OK, here's the mission.

00:20:31.700 --> 00:20:33.000 align:middle line:90%
It's humans to Mars.

00:20:33.000 --> 00:20:35.080 align:middle line:90%
What do we need to do that?

00:20:35.080 --> 00:20:36.630 align:middle line:90%
And then you do those things.

00:20:36.630 --> 00:20:39.210 align:middle line:84%
Since this movie was
composed, they've

00:20:39.210 --> 00:20:41.280 align:middle line:84%
come up with a new
hobby horse, which

00:20:41.280 --> 00:20:44.130 align:middle line:84%
is to put a space
station in lunar orbit,

00:20:44.130 --> 00:20:47.500 align:middle line:84%
