Mars, you go to Mars.

00:21:33.690 --> 00:21:38.540 align:middle line:84%
So, basically, what we need
is a mission driven program.

00:21:38.540 --> 00:21:40.510 align:middle line:84%
I mean, the way to
think about it is--

00:21:40.510 --> 00:21:42.093 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And what
do you mean by that?

00:21:42.093 --> 00:21:45.810 align:middle line:84%
>>ZUBRIN: Well OK, let's
think of two couples.

00:21:45.810 --> 00:21:48.510 align:middle line:84%
