00:22:29.730 --> 00:22:31.830 align:middle line:84%
And then they invite
the in-laws over.

00:22:31.830 --> 00:22:35.310 align:middle line:84%
And then pa-in-law says to
son-in-law, why do you have

00:22:35.310 --> 00:22:37.289 align:middle line:90%
