we learned how to drill for it

00:43:04.910 --> 00:43:08.180 align:middle line:84%
and refine it and make machines
that could use the product.

00:43:08.180 --> 00:43:10.460 align:middle line:84%
Uranium was not a
resource until we learned

00:43:10.460 --> 00:43:12.510 align:middle line:90%
how to do nuclear energy.

00:43:12.510 --> 00:43:16.490 align:middle line:84%
There's all sorts
of stuff on Mars.

00:43:16.490 --> 00:43:20.270 align:middle line:84%
